Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:04.91,Chihiro,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 说到下雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:10.14,Keima,,0000,0000,0000,,告白定在明日放学后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:11.83,Keima,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:16.74,Chihiro,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
